      "mentorSays": "At the end of this lesson, you will be able to:\n\n1. Understand what Decode Ways asks for\n2. Use dynamic programming to count ways\n3. Handle single and double digit decoding\n4. Check valid encoding (1-26)\n5. Implement the solution step by step in your chosen language",
